---
By: Han Shan
Source:
  ISBN: 1556591403
  Locus:
    Page: 191
  Publisher: Copper Canyon Press
  Title: The Collected Songs of Cold Mountain
  Translator: Red Pine
---
The Great Sea has no limit
fishes and dragons by the billion
everyone eating someone else
busy stupid lumps of flesh

because the mind never stops
delusions rise like mist
the moon of out nature is clear and bright
in the open it shines without limit
